msgid "Related areas in the PRAIS 4 platform: table SO2-3.T3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO2.md:334
msgid "Observed changes in the indicator and their interpretation may be described in the “Qualitative Assessment” table of the PRAIS 4 platform (table SO2-3.T3)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO2.md:336
msgid "It is important to note that changes in the proportion of population exposure to land degradation may not only be due to the expansion of land degradation but also to population growth, among other factors."
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO2.md:338
msgid "Step 5:  Verify the results"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO2.md:340
msgid "The reliability of the estimates from global data sources requires inputs from national experts to identify and highlight situations where the confidence level of the obtained results might be low."
msgstr ""

